  "summaries": [
    {
      "actionDate": "2025-02-14",
      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p><strong>Automotive Support Services to Improve Safe Transportation Act of 2025 or the ASSIST Act of 2025</strong></p><p>This bill expands the definition of <em>medical services</em> for purposes of veterans\u2019 benefits to include additional medically necessary automobile&nbsp;adaptations. Under the bill, the Department of Veterans Affairs may provide funding for ramp and kneeling systems, lowered floors, mobility device lifts, non-articulating trailers, and ingress or egress accessibility modifications.&nbsp;</p>",
      "updateDate": "2025-05-07T23:46:43Z",
      "versionCode": "00"
    }
  ]
